data.title: Tracking 150 People Who Crossed the Oceans
data.text:
Searching Names

The people involved with the Iwakura Mission can be broken down into three categories: delegation participants, in absentia government officials, and foreigners attached to the Mission. Those individuals who have a URL link to their name can be tracked through the results of a search through the materials. Users can also view an organizational chart and commentary in regard to the organizations to which these individuals were respectively attached.
